}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \ul0 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 141-142.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   The protagonist's }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 novo pensiero }{\plain \fs24 \f1 (new thought) has puzzled his commentators.  \softline
Is it one triggered by what he has seen and heard?  Or is he anticipating the matters he will \softline
